        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 text-xs font-bold">
          Lv.2
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs font-bold">
