          <div class="p-4 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Firebase Auth Recommended</h3>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Already using Firebase ecosystem (Firestore, etc.)</li>
              <li>Developing web + mobile simultaneously</li>
              <li>Need unlimited free users</li>
              <li>Google Sign-In is the primary method</li>
            </ul>
