            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth/web/manage-users" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">
                User Management
              </a> - Profile updates, password reset
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://firebase.google.com/docs/firestore" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">
                Firestore Integration
              </a> - Store per-user data
            </li>
          </ul>
        </Callout>
      </section>
    </article>

